Package com.dhemery.strings

Operate on strings and translate them to other types.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BooleanValue Translates a string to a Boolean.
ByteValue Translates a string to a Byte.
CharacterValue Translates a string to a Character.
DoubleValue Translates a string to a Double.
FloatValue Translates a string to a Float.
IntegerValue Translates a string to an Integer.
LongValue Translates a string to a Long.
ShortValue Translates a string to a Short.
Trimmed Trims whitespace from the start and end of a string.
WithoutPrefix Removes a prefix from a string.
WithoutSuffix Removes a suffix from a string.
WithPrefix Prepends a prefix to a string that lacks the prefix.
WithSuffix Appends a suffix to a string that lacks the suffix.
 

Package com.dhemery.strings Description

Operate on strings and translate them to other types.
